{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"adff9d2a57","title":"对章士钊来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd992c5d9b","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":5,"articleId":"adff9d2a57"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"6580264fa4","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"政协全国委员会常委、中央文史研究馆馆长章士钊1959年7月3日给毛泽东写信说：“硕得湘潭刘柏荣书，甚为惊说。此君名朴，所治确如朴学，性分不甚高而用力极勤。钊不得柏荣消息已三年，悠您罗月，始终见据于文史馆门篇之外，殊难索解。章士钊将刘柏荣给他的信转给毛泽东，请求一阅。刘柏荣，原为四川大学教授，后调入四川文史研究馆工作。"},{"id":"154d24253c","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李井泉，当时任中共四川省委第一书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"81f687f201","type":"title","text":"对章士钉来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57"},{"id":"6580264fa4","type":"paragraph","text":"井泉P同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57"},{"id":"154d24253c","type":"paragraph","text":"信三件，请看一下。回去，着四川文史馆负责人认真处理一下。如无大不妥处，宜予吸收，使其整理所学，较为有益。如何，请酯办。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57"},{"id":"78e7a57e6a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57"},{"id":"1ab2489ac7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年七月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57"}],"page":{"id":"53b3d74506","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"adff9d2a57","start":175,"end":175}}}},"__N_SSG":true}